@node "History" "The History of Ascii View"
                              @{B}History@{UB}
                              @{B}-------@{UB}

Version 1.0

First release. Only had view option.

Version 2.0

Second release, which implemented the two modes, to allow you to see the keys for the ASCII codes you enter. This function was suggested by Frank Bunton. Thank you!

@endnode

