@node "Other Products" "Other products Available By The Author"
                         @{B}Other Products From The Author@{UB}
                         @{B}------------------------------@{UB}

StartupDate (Amiga) : A program to allow you to set the date on Startup. Freeware. Available from Aminet.

ASCII View (Amiga)  : A Program to display ASCII codes of the keys you press. Freeware. Available from Aminet.

ASCII View (DOS)    : PC Version of ASCII view. Freeware. 

ASCII View (Windows): Windows (95 and 3.1) version of ASCII view. Freeware

NOTE : At the moment the Amiga version is the only version that allows you to see the keys of ASCII codes you enter. This may change soon!

Coming soon - ASCII View for UNIX. This will be released as Public domain with source code for use under different versions of UNIX. There will also be executable files for use with Linux and IRIX. Other versions will probably need the GNU C++ Compiler, G++.
@endnode
